</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_342" id="170r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_342_r1l5">Andres vogt von Ryneck <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l6">ʒu karlburg vnd karlſtat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_342_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Andres als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht ʒu vns geſandt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l8">habt von des pfeͣrds <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ Jr <expan>Jm<ex>m</ex></expan> her vor Sacʒ <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lorn</expan> ſüllt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l9">haben etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Nu als wır Raban hof = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l10">wart <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>wırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>hofmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l11">
<add><ab facs="#facs_342_r1l12">wır erfarn <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ </ab></add> <expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / daſelbs <expan>Jm<ex>m</ex></expan> her eın pferd <expan>ʒugeloffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / dıe vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l14"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> / wer 
<add><ab facs="#facs_342_line_1577278762825_2033">ʒu vns </ab></add> keͣm der ware wortʒaıche ſaget / Dem <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l15">ſıe das pferd <expan>wıdergebe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo haben wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht geweıſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l16">das pferd ʒubeſehen / vnd hett er es wellen <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> ſo <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> es Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l17">geben <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . ſo hat er vns geſagt daʒ es eẅr pferd niht ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l18">Alſo haben wır darnach fragen laſſen vnd <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> niht erfarn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l22">
<add>daʒ von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ </del> kein <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> pfeͣrd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> bey vns vorhanden </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_342_line_1577278780740_2055">aufgefangen </ab></add> ſey / denn daſſelb pferd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l23">daʒ man <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> hat ſehen laſſen / VVölt Jr <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l25">ʒu vns <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / das pferd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_342_r1l24">bas </ab></add> ʒubeſehen / ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l26"><expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürderlıch darcʒuſeın als vıl vns gebürt / Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_line_1577278797663_2078">wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l30">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Om<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_r1l31">Dıe antwurt <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> knecht geben haben ſo hat er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_342_line_1577278811718_2092">dıe niht wellen nemen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Jn <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> <expan>Om<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_342" id="170r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Andres Vogt von Ryneck, <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan>
                                                zu Karlburg und Karlstat</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Andres, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht zu uns gesandt
                                                habt, von des pfeͣrds <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                daz ir <expan>im<ex>m</ex></expan> her vor Sacz
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lorn</expan> süllt haben etc.,
                                                das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                                Nu als wir Raban Hofwart,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von
                                                  <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, nehst
                                                  <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie <add>wir erfarn
                                                  <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz</add>
<expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> daselbs
                                                  <expan>im<ex>m</ex></expan> her ein pferd
                                                  <expan>zugeloffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, die uns
                                                  <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>, wer <add>zu
                                                  uns</add> keͣm, der ware worczaiche saget, dem
                                                  <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> sie das pferd
                                                  <expan>widergebe<ex>n</ex></expan>, also haben wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht geweiset das
                                                pferd zu besehen und hett er es wellen
                                                  <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan>, so
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> es im geben
                                                  <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, so hat er uns
                                                gesagt, daz es ewr pferd niht sey. Also haben wir
                                                darnach fragen lassen und
                                                  <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> niht erfarn,
                                                  <add>daz von den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add> kein
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> pfeͣrd
                                                  <add>aufgefangen</add> sey, denn dasselb pferd,
                                                daz man <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> hat sehen lassen.
                                                Wölt ir <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu uns
                                                  <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, das pferd
                                                  <add>bas</add> zu besehen, so
                                                  <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürderlich darczusein,
                                                als vil uns gebürt. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc. Die
                                                antwurt <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> knecht geben haben,
                                                so hat er die niht wellen nemen.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                                                  <expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
